{"tid":102772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"司機冇鎖車門瞌一瞌　南亞賊伺機偷竊被捕","createTime":"2017-01-31T23:30:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T10:19:59.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"68aa0633397c19759b2a1e746d1e7f2d081e3310","tid":102772,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T23:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170201/photo/bkn-20170201060220946-0201_00822_001_01b.jpg?20170201070047\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170201%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170201060220946-0201_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20170201070047&h=3a0ab116&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n司機在場協助調查，案件車輛停泊在砵蘭街對出位置。(葉嘉文攝)<br />\n<br />\n旺角大意司機成賊人目標！清晨5時許，一名姓彭男子駕駛七人車停泊在砵蘭街380號對開瞌一瞌，一名南亞裔男子突然打開後座車門，偷走一件外套，一部HTC手提電話及一個袋後速閃，司機發現隨即落車追截，並高呼求救，剛巧有巡警發現加入追捕，南亞漢跑至200米外近彌敦道旺角警署對出被擒獲。警員於其身上尋回被偷去的外套及袋，惟手提電話疑賊人逃跑時棄掉。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170201/photo/bkn-20170201060220946-0201_00822_001_02b.jpg?20170201070047\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170201%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170201060220946-0201_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20170201070047&h=6214183e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姓彭司機協助調查。(葉嘉文攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170201/photo/bkn-20170201060220946-0201_00822_001_03b.jpg?20170201070047\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170201%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170201060220946-0201_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20170201070047&h=e3317d19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當時司機正在車輛中休息。(葉嘉文攝)<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170201/photo/bkn-20170201060220946-0201_00822_001_04b.jpg?20170201070047\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170201%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170201060220946-0201_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20170201070047&h=d2294a6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170201/bkn-20170201060220946-0201_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170201%2Fbkn-20170201060220946-0201_00822_001.html&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=7c8c90c3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170201/bkn-20170201060220946-0201_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8b8cbf81d78bac264b73cde0b1b2bbbbb52a2850","tid":102772,"uid":28644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T23:36:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7045604e7950c13c793a4c76d67a5d6856aec66","tid":102772,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:19:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}